Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
Has the submitted form been sent to the server? The current page is a demonstration form and will not be uploaded to the server; Please use email for formal communication.
Does the tool save my data? The on-site tools should be run on the local browser first. For details, please refer to the Privacy Policy.
Does it support custom development? Welcome to describe your requirements and scenarios through email, we will evaluate and provide feedback.